    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the humanitarian side, but looking at the long term... doesn't the fact that it basically broke the country and created a power vacuum make the whole thing a strategic failure? like, if the goal was regional stability, it clearly did the opposite.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
